<BaseLayout title="About — Doug Standley">
  <article>
    <h1>About</h1>
    <p>
      Doug is a designer-operator-builder who enters where emerging technology is becoming mandatory, but lacks the operating model to be adopted. Over three decades, he has built at that boundary: founding Deloitte Digital, running an 18-company broadcast roll-up integrated into a public offering, and developing a distributed-intelligence platform whose nine patents advanced through acquisition discussions with Google.
    </p>
    <p>
      His focus today is AI — not in theory, but in deployment — where adoption fails, constraints dominate, and governance is still being invented.
    </p>
  </article>
